      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch anywhere! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that's basically brand new, this is the one. Can't wait for you to see it!",
